### 1. List all study topics
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/topics/
Accept: application/json

### 2. Create a new study topic
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/topics/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Master FastAPI Foundations",
  "description": "Learn routing, dependencies, and Pydantic validation for EX1",
  "status": "todo"
}

### 3. Update a topic (Change the ID '1' to match an actual topic ID)
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:8000/topics/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "in_progress",
  "is_favorite": true
}

### 4. Delete a topic (Change the ID '1' to match an actual topic ID)
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/topics/1